data.description: Well maintained, updated Merion Village duplex with 2 side by side units, each with 1,020 Square Feet & offering 3 Bedrooms & 1-1/2 Baths. Full Front Porch, & 43 x 134 corner property with alley access to the 20x30 3-bay Garage. Each side features a Living Room with hardwood flooring & decorative fireplace, Dining Room with stairs to upper level, & a fully applianced, remodeled Kitchen with white cabinets & vinyl flooring. Back entry area with Half Bath & sliding glass door to the fenced yard. 3 upper level BRs & Full Bath complete the layout of each unit. Separate Basement areas with washer/dryer & storage space. Updates include: Roof & HVAC (2019), freshly painted interior, new Half Baths, lighting & more. Convenient to elementary school, bus lines, shopping, High St. Great Investment!
